	    	<h2>What?</h2>
	    	<p>Simple, write your presentation using the <a href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax">markdown syntax</a> and generate an awesome HTML5 slide show like Google's <a href="http://slides.html5rocks.com/">HTML5Rocks presentation</a>.</p>
	    	<p>This project is heavily inspired in the ruby <a href="http://slideshow.rubyforge.org/">Slide Show (S9)</a> project.</p>
	    	<p>The difference is that you can use this from the browser, while S9 is a command-line utiliy.</p>
	    	
